M|references|**LinkedIn-specific guidelines:**
M|references|- Professional tone, but not boring
M|references|- Use job-specific language the audience recognizes
M|references|- Statistics and data points perform well
M|references|- Avoid consumer-style hype ("Amazing!" "Incredible!")
M|references|- First-person testimonials from peers resonate
