M|references|**TikTok-specific guidelines:**
M|references|- Native cnt outperforms polished ads
M|references|- First 2 seconds determine if they watch
M|references|- Use trending sounds and formats
M|references|- Text overlay is essential (most watch with sound off)
M|references|- Vertical video only (9:16)
